-- Government Activates Emergency Group Aimed at Maintaining Fuel Supplies
-- B y   V i d y a   R o o t
-- 2010-10-18T10:57:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-18/government-activates-emergency-group-aimed-at-maintaining-fuel-supplies.html
The French government activated an
emergency crisis cell aimed at maintaining fuel supplies after
striking workers shut down refineries and blocked oil depots,
the interior ministry said on its website.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vidya Root at 
 vroot@bloomberg.net  